                    <div class="answer-content">
                        <p><strong>Solution:</strong></p>
                        <p>299,800,000 m/s = 2.998 × 10⁸ m/s</p>
                        <p>Since we're given "approximately" and the number ends in zeros, we should consider how many figures are truly known.</p>
